    DOCTRINE["вљ  PLATFORM DOCTRINE\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nAI may advise. AI may explain.\nAI may optimize. AI may correlate.\nAI may recommend.\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nAI may NOT authoritatively govern.\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nEnforcement authority belongs\nexclusively to the\nDeterministic Governance Plane."]:::doctrine

    subgraph OUTPUT_LAYER["в‘Ґ DECISION OUTPUT LAYER  В·  Universal Contract"]
        direction LR
        DEC["Decision Envelope\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\nALLOW В· DENY В· WARN В· OVERRIDE_REQUIRED\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\ndecision_id В· timestamp В· reason\ntrace В· suggestions В· override_required"]:::contract
        EXIT["Exit Code Contract\nв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ\n0 = ALLOW\n1 = DENY\n2 = WARN\n3 = OVERRIDE_REQUIRED"]:::contract
    end

    subgraph STORE_LAYER["в‘¦ STORAGE LAYER  В·  Local-First  В·  No Cloud Dependency for Enforcement"]
        direction LR
        LFS["Local Filesystem\nDecision Artifacts В· Audit Logs В· Traces"]:::storage
        VCS["VCS Policy Store\nGit-Native Policy Management"]:::storage
        SAAS["Future В· SaaS Control Plane\nCentralized Policy В· Dashboard\nMulti-Team Governance В· Analytics"]:::future
    end

    INPUTS --> CLI_LAYER
    CLI_LAYER --> EXEC_LAYER
    EXEC_LAYER --> DGP
    DGP --> OUTPUT_LAYER
    PIP --> OUTPUT_LAYER
    OUTPUT_LAYER --> STORE_LAYER

    BIN --> REG
    REG --> DISP
    DISP --> VERDICT
    DISP -.-> SEC
    DISP -.-> COMP
    DISP -.-> IDENT
    DISP -.-> ARCHL
    DISP -.-> AIG

    TFP --> VERDICT
    POLF --> DSL

    DEC --> LFS
    DEC --> VCS
    LFS -.-> SAAS

    DGP -. "enforces\nnever delegated to AI" .-> DOCTRINE
    PIP -. "advises only\nnever enforces" .-> DOCTRINE
